# Root .dockerignore — applied to every build context unless a more specific
# `<Dockerfile>.dockerignore` overrides it.

# Build outputs and caches
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/coverage
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Logs and OS junk
*.log
**/*.log
.DS_Store

# VCS and CI
.git
.github

# Local env files — never bake into images. Keep .env.example so apps that
# document required envs at build time can still resolve them.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Repo docs / agent rules (not needed inside any image)
**/CLAUDE.md
**/audit.md

# Tests
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.e2e-spec.ts
**/*.test.ts
